{"tid":882634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王曦彥及伍嘉儀鬧市馬路攔巴士判服務令及感化令 官：舉動自私罔顧他人福祉","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T14:57:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08f7b8c220fbdafe513b41de96153bde139e1880","tid":882634,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853613&d=%2Bi4EYpcX0ygC0tY6g2C%2Fs9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6cf62e64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853613&h=3a736d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853613</a><br />\n<br />\n情侶去年10月因不滿巴士飛站，衝出銅鑼灣崇光百貨對開馬路攔阻巴士，他們早前被裁定對公共交通造成阻礙罪名成立。裁判官今判刑時強調，法庭不鼓勵任何打出捍衛自身權益的旗號，卻自私、罔顧他人福祉的舉動，認為需判處阻嚇性刑罰，但接納兩人有悔意，判男被告接受140小時社會服務令，女被告則接受12個月感化。<br />\n<br />\n早前求情時稱經營補習學校的男被告王曦彥（29歲），及報稱任家庭主婦的女被告伍嘉儀（30歲），早前被裁定於去年10月6日，在銅鑼灣軒尼詩道555號崇光百貨外，無合法權限或解釋，妨礙其他道路使用者，令公共交通受阻礙罪成。男被告另被控普通襲擊罪則罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時表示，本案性質有別於一般同類案件，兩被告在周五晚上的香港鬧市，因上不到巴士而阻礙巴士前進，任何合理人士都明知這會對公眾造成影響。<br />\n裁判官續指，案發時男被告率先衝出馬路，其後更拍打巴士車身和指罵司機，行為涉及暴力；至於女被告，裁判官指她稍後才加入阻礙交通行列，考慮到女被告沒有案底和及其背景，判女被告感化令，官並叮囑她須依從感化官指示，接受精神及心理治療、參加社區活動和群組等。<br />\n<br />\n男被告代表律師今進一步求情時，形容男被告的社會服務令報告及感化令報告評價均正面，又引述報告形容男被告態度真誠、合作。男被告亦承認曾阻礙別人，希望向受影響的人致歉。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：ESCC101/18】<br />\n<br />\n記者鄭語霆"},{"pid":"4388dcb362f616f224b60fcf142b3b279e57bce8","tid":882634,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"熱狗勇武擋巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5839f9c9bc3a900cf6fbec5fbde1beae3d8376b9","tid":882634,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83312096e4d3e855f584a9f7f61189dda5b75273","tid":882634,"uid":96894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4388dcb362f616f224b60fcf142b3b279e57bce8","tid":882634,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"熱狗勇武擋巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/132719_e10089de73b4cf8196f28e40dd96094f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F132719_e10089de73b4cf8196f28e40dd96094f.jpg&h=c7f45052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/133032_b3c3d1972bf4725fb19d31d66ff4bc42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F133032_b3c3d1972bf4725fb19d31d66ff4bc42.jpg&h=b035bae2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}